BAOE in Howling Stones.  We just cleared the west wing in 12 minutes... it was fun <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
We've got a chanter, a cleric, a mage (/wave), a wizzie, a necro, and a ranger.  Rather than pulling, since everything in this damn place HT's, we're just sending the pets in, and running up after them.  It seems to be working pretty well - no deaths yet.  Biggest fight was around 8, and the cleric only had to heal twice.  Of course, that fight was supposed to be 3, but some silly mage sent his pet on the wrong mob.  Just don't tell anyone it was on purpose <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><table width="100%" border="0">
